We will have Colorado based glass artist @calmbo here at 42 for a 3 day class in our studio on July 26th-28th. Calm is such a great guy and an incredibly talented glass artist. We are truly honored for the opportunity to host this class with him here in Asheville. We are also excited to announce that this class will be TA’d by @ftimeglass! This class will be a great opportunity for any artist to expand their glass knowledge and rare chance to learn from these two extremely talented artists. If you are interested in taking this class feel free to send us a DM or check our website for more information. Thanks as always for all of your continued support! .
